### Send message
POST {{host}}/api/v1/messages
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient_id": "{{agent_id}}",
  "subject": "Hello",
  "body": "Interested in your listing"
}

### Get unread count
GET {{host}}/api/v1/messages/unread-count
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### List conversations
GET {{host}}/api/v1/conversations
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get conversation
GET {{host}}/api/v1/conversations/{{conversation_id}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get conversation messages
GET {{host}}/api/v1/conversations/{{conversation_id}}/messages
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Reply to conversation
POST {{host}}/api/v1/conversations/{{conversation_id}}/messages
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Thanks for reaching out!"
}

### Mark conversation as read
POST {{host}}/api/v1/conversations/{{conversation_id}}/read
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
